<br>
<br>
The issues on our list that we got answers on are:<br>
<br>
<br>
    *<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
      The ability to hold agro - There are no plans to give Bards any kind of snap agro at this time.<br>
<br>
    *<br>
<br>
