<br>
<br>
Also, the 10th slot on our top 10 list is going to float. Every month Im going to personally choose an issue that will slide into that spot. Bug fixes, minor issues (Such as Steadfast Servant poofing when we Fade), and small requests will slide in there. I will make sure to bring up my choice in serverwide.bards<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ards so that people can give me feedback on my choice and maybe change my mind. I will decide which issue I want to put in here after voting has concluded.<br>
<br>
<br>
